<i>noun</i>: 광기 [광끼] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>광기 [광끼]</dt><br>
<dd>1. madness</dd><br>
<dd>미친 듯한 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>A crazy-like spirit.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lunacy</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 미친 것처럼 마구 덤비며 거칠게 행동하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) An act of assaulting or acting roughly as if crazy.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>